  "stem": "<p>The graph shows the predicted value <i>y</i>, in dollars, of a commercial drone <i>x</i> years after it is first purchased.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><figure class='image'><svg role=\"img\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 360 320\" width=\"360\" height=\"320\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"Graph showing the value of a drone in dollars decreasing over time in years. The curve passes through (0, 30000) and (4, 7500).\"><defs><style>.ax{stroke:#333;stroke-width:1.2;fill:none}.gr{stroke:#ddd;stroke-width:0.6;fill:none}.cv{stroke:#1f77b4;stroke-width:2;fill:none}.pt{fill:#1f77b4}.lb{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;fill:#222}</style></defs><rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"360\" height=\"320\" fill=\"#fff\"/><g class=\"gr\"><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"170\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"230\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"230\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"290\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"40\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"100\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"160\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"160\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"220\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"280\"/></g><g class=\"ax\"><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"310\" y2=\"280\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"280\"/></g><path class=\"cv\" d=\"M 50 40 Q 110 130 170 200 T 290 260\"/><circle class=\"pt\" cx=\"50\" cy=\"40\" r=\"3.5\"/><circle class=\"pt\" cx=\"230\" cy=\"220\" r=\"3.5\"/><text class=\"lb\" x=\"58\" y=\"38\">(0, 30000)</text><text class=\"lb\" x=\"238\" y=\"218\">(4, 7500)</text><text class=\"lb\" x=\"170\" y=\"305\">Years after purchase</text><text class=\"lb\" x=\"5\" y=\"160\" transform=\"rotate(-90 15,160)\">Value ($)</text></svg></figure></p><p>Based on the graph, what was the value of the drone at the time it was purchased?</p>",
